---
Checks: >
  -*,
  bugprone-*,
  cert-*,
  clang-analyzer-*,
  misc-*,
  performance-*,
  portability-*,
  readability-*,
  -readability-identifier-length,
  -bugprone-easily-swappable-parameters

HeaderFilterRegex: '.*'

CheckOptions:
  readability-braces-around-statements.ShortStatementLines: 1
...